Okie just checked the source code and Babu will only make a band name out of messages that have at least 2 words and no more than 6 words. Each time a message between 2-6 words is posted, Babu has a 1/1000 chance of turning it into a band name. Each time a message of the specified length is posted, the odds are slightly increased. The exact odds are 1 / (1000 - numFails*0.5) where numFails is the number of messages between 2-6 words that didn't successfully make a band name. numFails resets to zero every time there's a successful band name made (edited)
